Question: What kind of fruit is the white kitten playing with, an apple or a banana?

Reference Answer: banana

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n567860.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='kitten')
IMAGE0=CROP_BELOW(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='apple')
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='banana')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX1)
ANSWER1=COUNT(box=BOX2)
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'apple' if {ANSWER0} > {ANSWER1} else 'banana'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
